{"id":"REV.18.1-REV.18.24","orgId":"REV.18.1-REV.18.24","bibleId":"de4e12af7f28f599-02","bookId":"REV","chapterIds":["REV.18"],"reference":"Revelation 18:1-24","content":[{"name":"chapter","type":"tag","attrs":{"number":"18","style":"c","sid":"REV 18"},"items":[{"text":"18","type":"text"}]},{"name":"para","type":"tag","attrs":{"style":"p"},"items":[{"name":"verse-span","type":"tag","attrs":{"class":"verse-span","verseId":"REV.18.1","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.1"]},"items":[{"name":"verse","type":"tag","attrs":{"number":"1","style":"v","sid":"REV 18:1"},"items":[{"text":"1","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"verse-span","type":"tag","attrs":{"class":"verse-span","verseId":"REV.18.1","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.1"]},"items":[{"text":"And after these things I saw another angel come down from heaven, having great power; and the earth was lightened with his glory. ","type":"text","attrs":{"verseId":"REV.18.1","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.1"]}}]},{"name":"verse-span","type":"tag","attrs":{"class":"verse-span","verseId":"REV.18.2","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.2"]},"items":[{"name":"verse","type":"tag","attrs":{"number":"2","style":"v","sid":"REV 18:2"},"items":[{"text":"2","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"verse-span","type":"tag","attrs":{"class":"verse-span","verseId":"REV.18.2","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.2"]},"items":[{"text":"And he cried mightily with a strong voice, saying, Babylon the great is fallen, is fallen, and is become the habitation of devils, and the hold of every foul spirit, and a cage of every unclean and hateful bird. ","type":"text","attrs":{"verseId":"REV.18.2","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.2"]}}]},{"name":"verse-span","type":"tag","attrs":{"class":"verse-span","verseId":"REV.18.3","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.3"]},"items":[{"name":"verse","type":"tag","attrs":{"number":"3","style":"v","sid":"REV 18:3"},"items":[{"text":"3","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"verse-span","type":"tag","attrs":{"class":"verse-span","verseId":"REV.18.3","verseOrgIds":["REV.18.3"]},"items":[{"text":"For all nations have drunk of t